        "timestamp": "2018-09-20 15:59:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\n> (1 comment)\n > \n > Generaly I would recommend to try this on lab to avoid this kind of\n > problems.\n\nHi Kornel,\n\nWe have validated this blueprint on the dcae-cloudify-manager pod in our own ONAP environment. Also we don't think this container_port parameter is mandatory as k8s-ves.yaml-template also uses the node type ContainerizedPlatformComponent but doesn't use container_port. If this blueprint doesn't work in your lab environment we are happy to change it, but we are not sure on how to add two ports with the container_port parameter as this is required.",
